JSONpedia README
================

How to run the CLI:

Requirements:

  Maven 3.x+

Compile sources

  Some tests could fail preventing the building of the package
  in such case add the skip test flag (maven.test.skip):

     mvn [-Dmaven.test.skip=true] clean package

  This will generate a target dir containing generated files included

     target/jsonpedia-x.y-SNAPSHOT.jar

Run CLI

   java -cp target/jsonpedia-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.machinelinking.exporter.CSVExporterCLI

   Running without arguments will produce help info:
   Usage: <main class> [options]
     Options:
     * --in, -i        Input file
     * --out, -o       Output file
     * --prefix, -p    Page prefix
       --threads, -t   Number of threads
                       Default: 0

CLI Usage examples

   java -cp target/jsonpedia-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.machinelinking.exporter.CSVExporterCLI \
      -p http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki -i src/test/resources/enwiki-latest-pages-articles-p3.xml.gz -o out.csv

   Processing with 2 threads
   Closing process...
   Done.
   processor: Processed pages: 25, elapsed time: 0 (ms), exceptions: []
    templates: 1117, properties 4907, max properties/template: 52, avg properties/template: 4,393017

